nodes.text: Faedral was a male Human citizen of the Eternal Empire of Zakuul. Working as security for the Overwatch, in 3630 BBY he and a fellow hunter Zaamsk engaged the rogue terrorist Firebrand and The Commander at the power junction in Breaktown. However, the hunters were defeated and killed.
Faedral appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire Chapter 10: Anarchy in Paradise.
